 <i>consecutive years.</i>

00:03:53.233 --> 00:03:54.769 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>This time,</i>
 <i>they are here to win</i>

00:03:54.802 --> 00:03:56.303 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>the Triple Championship.</i>

00:03:56.336 --> 00:03:58.506 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>On the other hand,</i>
