 <i>and today,</i>
 <i>they're going to face</i>

00:04:02.143 --> 00:04:03.443 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>the current</i>
 <i>national champion.</i>

00:04:03.477 --> 00:04:05.046 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Will Nishikigaoka</i>
 <i>be able to</i>

00:04:05.079 --> 00:04:06.180 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>get a victory this time?</i>

