00:04:45.019 --> 00:04:46.286 position:19% line:89% align:start
Come, guys, let's go!

00:04:46.319 --> 00:04:47.789 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:04:47.822 --> 00:04:49.389 position:30% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
It looks like Tsubasa

