- <i>and sends a long pass</i>
-Go!

00:05:06.774 --> 00:05:07.407 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>to Nagano.</i>

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:08.709 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
Go!

