[announcer]
 <i>Nagano passes the ball</i>

00:05:10.310 --> 00:05:11.712 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>to their specialist, Taki.</i>
-[grunt]

00:05:11.746 --> 00:05:13.815 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>We don't know if</i>
 <i>he's planning on shooting.</i>

00:05:13.848 --> 00:05:16.284 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>What strategy is</i>
 <i>Nankatsu planning?</i>

00:05:16.316 --> 00:05:17.552 position:24% line:89% align:start
Mamoru, it's yours!

00:05:17.585 --> 00:05:19.787 position:27% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Taki passes
the ball to Izawa.

00:05:19.821 --> 00:05:20.888 position:19% line:89% align:start
We're counting on you.

00:05:20.922 --> 00:05:21.354 position:38% line:89% align:start
Teppei!

00:05:22.355 --> 00:05:24.659 position:16% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Izawa feints
and sends the pass,

00:05:24.692 --> 00:05:25.458 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>and Kisugi</i>

