 <i>Nankatsu scored</i>
 <i>the first goal of the match.</i>

00:05:32.700 --> 00:05:33.668 position:30% line:77% align:start
-Yeah!
-[announcer]
A great play

00:05:33.701 --> 00:05:35.303 position:38% line:77% align:start
-[laugh]
-
 <i>by Izawa and Taki</i>

00:05:35.335 --> 00:05:37.470 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>with the forward</i>
 <i>Kisugi from Nankatsu.</i>

00:05:37.505 --> 00:05:38.539 position:41% line:83% align:start
Yeah!
Good job!

00:05:38.573 --> 00:05:40.141 position:33% line:83% align:start
That's great!
The Shutetsu trio's

00:05:40.174 --> 00:05:41.042 position:30% line:89% align:start
done it again!

00:05:41.075 --> 00:05:42.543 position:19% line:89% align:start
Excellent work, guys.

00:05:42.577 --> 00:05:44.278 position:19% line:89% align:start
What an awesome goal.

00:05:44.312 --> 00:05:45.913 position:44% line:83% align:start
Mhm.
My good friends...

00:05:45.947 --> 00:05:47.548 position:35% line:89% align:start
Nankatsu!

00:05:47.582 --> 00:05:49.482 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Nankatsu!
-[grunts]

00:05:49.517 --> 00:05:50.685 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Nankatsu!
-[grunt] It's mine.

00:05:50.718 --> 00:05:52.419 position:13% line:83% align:start
