You just lost it.

00:05:52.452 --> 00:05:53.754 position:30% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
Ishizaki clears the area.

00:05:53.788 --> 00:05:54.722 position:41% line:89% align:start
Whoa!

00:05:54.755 --> 00:05:57.158 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] And Nankatsu's
defense shines!

00:05:57.191 --> 00:05:58.259 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Furuoya]
 <i>Good.</i>

00:05:58.292 --> 00:05:59.627 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're all focused</i>
 <i>and determined</i>

00:05:59.660 --> 00:06:02.296 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>to let their captain rest.</i>

00:06:02.330 --> 00:06:04.031 position:38% line:83% align:start
Mamoru!
Here!

00:06:04.065 --> 00:06:04.932 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:06:04.966 --> 00:06:05.900 position:30% line:89% align:start
Let's go back.

00:06:05.933 --> 00:06:07.735 position:19% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Nankatsu
is on the attack again,

00:06:07.768 --> 00:06:10.338 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and Nishikigaoka</i>
 <i>is unable to stop them.</i>

00:06:10.370 --> 00:06:11.639 position:35% line:89% align:start
My turn.

00:06:11.672 --> 00:06:13.074 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:06:13.608 --> 00:06:14.876 position:30% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
Goal!

00:06:14.909 --> 00:06:17.511 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Izawa was able to</i>
 <i>easily make his way through</i>

00:06:17.545 --> 00:06:19.780 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>and score</i>
 <i>the second goal.</i>

00:06:19.814 --> 00:06:20.581 position:35% line:89% align:start
