anything less from Nankatsu.

00:06:32.226 --> 00:06:33.594 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's almost like they...

00:06:33.628 --> 00:06:35.529 position:19% line:83% align:start
like they didn't have
any weak points.

00:06:35.563 --> 00:06:37.098 position:13% line:83% align:start
