going to be able

00:06:37.131 --> 00:06:38.833 position:30% line:83% align:start
to do anything
without Tsubasa,

00:06:38.866 --> 00:06:39.533 position:27% line:89% align:start
you were wrong.

00:06:39.567 --> 00:06:40.801 position:27% line:83% align:start
We're a complete
entire team.

00:06:40.835 --> 00:06:43.504 position:13% line:83% align:start
Now you will know the true
strength of Nankatsu.

00:06:43.537 --> 00:06:44.639 position:19% line:89% align:start
Let 'em see it, guys!

00:06:44.672 --> 00:06:46.406 position:24% line:83% align:start
Let's go, Nankatsu!
[laugh]

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:47.942 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:06:47.975 --> 00:06:49.110 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:06:49.143 --> 00:06:50.211 position:21% line:89% align:start
And to think we hide

00:06:50.244 --> 00:06:51.812 position:10% line:83% align:start
our special secret technique
from them

00:06:51.846 --> 00:06:54.081 position:24% line:83% align:start
just to make them
worry before the match.

00:06:54.115 --> 00:06:56.384 position:19% line:83% align:start
But seeing them play
like that, without Tsubasa,

00:06:56.416 --> 00:06:57.484 position:19% line:89% align:start
is making me nervous.

00:06:57.518 --> 00:06:58.853 position:16% line:83% align:start
